response.overview: "Jethro: Not For The Vicar" is a comedy special that features the inimitable humor of British comedian Jethro. In this uproarious performance, Jethro presents his trademark blend of rural wit, observational humor, and charming storytelling.  The special takes the audience on a humorous journey through the quirks and idiosyncrasies of rural life, offering a delightful glimpse into the world of the countryside. Jethro's humor is characterized by its down-to-earth style and his ability to find hilarity in the ordinary and everyday situations.
response.title: Jethro: Not For The Vicar
